# IBM Quantum credentials — copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is git-ignored.
#
# Get these from https://quantum.cloud.ibm.com/ after creating an account:
#   IBM_QUANTUM_TOKEN     — your API key
#   IBM_QUANTUM_INSTANCE  — the CRN of your instance (looks like "crn:v1:bluemix:public:...")
#
# Note: the older `ibm_quantum` channel and the `IBMQ` provider no longer exist; this
# project uses the current `ibm_quantum_platform` channel via qiskit-ibm-runtime.
#
# These are only needed for notebooks/03_hardware.ipynb. Everything else — the full test
# suite and all other notebooks — runs on the local simulator with no credentials.

IBM_QUANTUM_TOKEN=
IBM_QUANTUM_INSTANCE=
